lines.text: Don't worry Dale, I'll only stick it in halfway.
You thought you'd killed me Gordon, but my drive for lust and power is relentless! Your penis - and MY brain - will be a marriage, made in Hell!
You, as the possessor of the virile force, must make love to the Queen!
Dale... Dale, she's right. It must be done. Rumour has it she's quite a piece.
Doc's right, Dale. I'll only stick it in halfway.
